<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .header img {
      height: 100px;
      max-width: 200px;
      object-fit: contain;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333333;
    }
    h2, p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .highlight {
      background: #FFF4F4;
      padding: 15px;
      border-left: 4px solid #DC2626;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #EFF6FF;
      color: #000000;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .footer a {
      margin: 0 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer a img {
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      filter: invert(100%);
    }
    .footer a:hover img {
      filter: invert(70%);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <table role="presentation" class="container">
    <tr>
      <td class="header">
        <img src="cid:companyLogo" alt="{{companyName}} Logo" />
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{applicantName}},</h2>
        <div class="highlight">
          <p>We wanted to let you know that your application for the position of <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> at <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> has been withdrawn from our system.</p>
        </div>
        <p>This could have been due to one of the following reasons:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>You requested to withdraw your application.</li>
          <li>Our team processed a removal based on updated recruitment needs.</li>
          <li>Your profile no longer meets the job requirements.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If this withdrawal was unintentional or you believe it was made in error, please contact our recruitment team immediately at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a> so we can review the situation.</p>
        <p>You are always welcome to apply for other opportunities with <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>. You can browse open positions on our careers page here: <a href="{{careersPage}}" target="_blank">{{careersPage}}</a></p>
        <p>Thank you for your interest in joining our team, and we wish you the very best in your job search journey.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br /><strong>{{companyName}} Recruitment Team</strong></p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2025 {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/YourCompany" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <img src="cid:iconFacebook" alt="Facebook" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/YourCompany" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <img src="cid:iconTwitter" alt="Twitter" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/company/YourCompany" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <img src="cid:iconLinkedin" alt="LinkedIn" />
        </a>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
